HEADWORD: Obumbrate
<hw>Ob*um"brate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>obumbratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>obumbrare</ets> to overshadow,
cloud; <ets>ob + umbrare</ets> to shade.]</ety> <def>To shade; to
darken; to cloud.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
